title: Looking for members for semi serious team (Jungle, Support and Mid)
body:
Hey guys

Looking for members for a ranked 5's team who are semi serious to play quite often.
Would prefer anywhere from bronze - gold but if anyone higher wants to play with lower elos more then welcome.
We have a top laner and an adc. Don't ask to join if you want adc or top.

**_We use teamspeak 3 for communication not skype or curse voice!_**

Add Mr Tickles if you are interested or comment here

Cheers
(Oceania)

replies.body:
I would like to join
I main jg
I'd be willing to join as a mid laner if you haven't got one already
